{"tid":44390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個撞鬼經歷","createTime":"2016-12-18T08:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T10:35:34.000Z","uid":59610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6a86ded588c2d057df46f3b6b43403aa6aa2a4a","tid":44390,"uid":59610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:43:06.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一次發夢聽到一個男人同我講野，之後喺屋企張床訓醒左，心諗發惡夢。<br />\n<br />\n點知成身郁唔到，小弟不嬲知道俾鬼壓係有科學解釋，本來都諗住冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知又聽到喺夢入面果個男人同我講左聲hi, 我已經嚇撚到標屎，但係郁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住佢勁大聲話[我同你講緊野呀！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身有信教，係撚咁喺心入面講屌你老母屌你老母！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住先突然郁得番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇諗過屋企都撞野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過講粗口真係好撚有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴打有冇咩特別經驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77262298b45e1d6d10c50eab48669f28bbc519bd","tid":44390,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從未撞過鬼"},{"pid":"d691046851868fa3c018401cb0de8cb26849f536","tid":44390,"uid":10821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從未撞過鬼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個經尸一 每個post都見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7290ef9ec301d42d6fa4e57b1c341854cb0d59d","tid":44390,"uid":10821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T08:55:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從未撞過鬼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個經<span style=\"color: red;\">歷</span> 每個post都見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"76b08e9f6acf8382c3dce53d6b1f053fdae42d4d","tid":44390,"uid":59610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從未撞過鬼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁巴打信唔信有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbee15ab4b9f1a070030e140ff3d17346dcb5f63","tid":44390,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從未撞過鬼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁巴打信唔信有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算信嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔想見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254f5035916f6391e3743ca1f3a425ebede57c8b","tid":44390,"uid":31859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:01:36.000Z","msg":"留明先"},{"pid":"dac96b07d3aa97b